description:
In this karaoke version of Turn your eyes upon Jesus, you'll join me in worshiping the Lord with some amazing Gospel music!
Whether you're looking for a fun way to celebrate Easter or just want to jam out to some amazing music, this gospel karaoke video is perfect for you! From classics to recent hits, this video has something for everyone! So turn your eyes up towards Jesus and join me in worshiping Him with your voice!

3 Sisters Youtube Production!

chapters.title: TURN YOUR EYES UPON JESUS (Classic Hymn)
O soul, are you weary and troubled?
No light in the darkness you see?
There's light for a look at the Savior
And life more abundant and free!
Look full in His wonderful face
And the things of earth will grow strangely dim
In the light of His glory and grace.
Then go to a world that is dying
